{"tid":1452622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武唔洗停 但要慎重重組戰術","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:50:18.000Z","uid":216332,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"46a428ec2f28d446795e013763da6fce1195ecd2","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"琴日睇得出真係輸戰術 同埋多鬼滲透<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸一日唔代表成場運動輸晒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n千奇要重組戰術 但真係唔好喺連登討論 呢到都俾鬼滲透得好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我唔識戰術呢D野 真係要搵識既人幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出面話咩勇武要停 係咪on9 不嬲呢場運動一開始都話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勝利formula= 和理非遊行 -&gt; deadline -&gt; 勇武</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"234f00c4409acd8b56bec1ffa7a7e5364d4baed2","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:29.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"59862e997a99502d6e5aea122ed60fc349e7dee1","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:39.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"dabaff6ccb60ca787bcab8e33e599078001712f2","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:49.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"9bd9af3d564fbc12eb4efd77db8ce7c033e7a1b7","tid":1452622,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:53:27.000Z","msg":"#讀者提供資訊 <br />\n<br />\n整咗封email 去國際刑事法院<br />\notp.informationdesk@icc-cpi.int<br />\n要求調查及控告香港警察， 請考慮一齊send！<br />\n（歡迎修改及轉載）<br />\n<br />\nRequest for investigation and prosecution of the HONG KONG POLICE FORCE<br />\n<br />\nDear Sirs,<br />\n<br />\nI would like to report that during the past few months, there were frequent demonstrations in Hong Kong by the local citizens, which were initiated to object the Extradition Bill proposed by the Hong Kong Government.<br />\n<br />\nDuring the demonstrations, the Hong Kong Police used unreasonable brutal forces / violence to disperse and arrest the demonstrators, including physical attacks, tear gas and plastic bullets.<br />\n<br />\nAs identified and verified by the demonstrators, tear gas used by the Hong Kong Police were well past the Expiry date and we understand that expired tear gas is actually toxic or harmful to health.<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong SAR government refused and keep on refusing to form an independent investigation committee to investigate the current turmoil as well as the seemingly unlawful acts done by the police police force.<br />\n<br />\nIn this regard, I would like to seek your assistance to instigate investigation into the unlawful enforcement of the Hong Kong Police, including the use of expired tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nThank you for your kind attention. I hope by your international impartial status as well as the connection with the UN, you can help us to stop the violence and offences being done by the HK Police, and bring true justice to us.<br />\n<br />\nRegards,<br />\n<br />\nXXXX<br />\nA Hong Kong citizen"},{"pid":"e6c01a5d9844e4bb2ea328723927188551404801","tid":1452622,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"我估樓主意思<br />\n例子:和理非&gt;唔回應&gt;殺1個警<br />\n係咁?<br />\n<br />\n請勇武小心留言"},{"pid":"fef993a92a5f22c9eb505cc015eea0b2832ee73d","tid":1452622,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:55:14.000Z","msg":"首先要重組<br />\n然後再諗下點練班新兵"},{"pid":"a9f0a81468835d12e890007a686250d93f9445fa","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:22:32.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"993cb8e4e3d81524d2397be7b2c96eba14cf0ee3","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6c01a5d9844e4bb2ea328723927188551404801","tid":1452622,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"我估樓主意思<br />\n例子:和理非&gt;唔回應&gt;殺1個警<br />\n係咁?<br />\n<br />\n請勇武小心留言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:23:45.000Z","msg":"殺警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個會咁有勇氣<br />\n重組戰術同武力升級唔同呀搞清楚<br />\n同埋示威者可以點武力升級呀我想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a29bdd350459ba21d1987eed5f997fe77b1102f","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef993a92a5f22c9eb505cc015eea0b2832ee73d","tid":1452622,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:55:14.000Z","msg":"首先要重組<br />\n然後再諗下點練班新兵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"戰術真係好緊要 人地訓練有素 示威者就一盤散沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e32ee04c1eff8f4c01ee7cda32c5cb1b092035","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b00051683d541a57ea2a3f6ba6adba428c6916d0","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"2fb69618ecb09b36f8ba8e7eb39e5e3a767a39bb","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"停乜撚野勇武"},{"pid":"49a4abe435c6cefa97f668d414999fd2197c4996","tid":1452622,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:01:18.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"62161063eb33867fec2116a6644aaac23a93e0d5","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"7ad5c29fb56be7b1b9e3114aa17ab656f5b54072","tid":1452622,"uid":216332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"